        <item>
            <title>首批 PS5 Pro Enhanced 遊戲揭曉　完整發揮新機效能</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/11/ps5-pro-enhanced/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ps5-pro-enhanced</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/11/ps5-pro-enhanced/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 16:16:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1262225</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>剛剛的「特別技術展示」雖然公佈了全新 PS5 Pro 主機，但並沒有透露任何的新遊戲。取而代之的是透露了首批可以完整發揮新機效能的「PS5 Pro Enhanced」遊戲。<br /><span id="more-1262225"></span></p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262227" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>首批支援 PS5 Pro Enhanced 功能的遊戲包括了不少 PS5 大作和之前已公佈的新作品。其中已推出的作品包括：</p><ul><li>《Alan Wake 2》</li><li>《Demon&#8217;s Souls》重製版</li><li>《Dragon&#8217;s Dogma 2》</li><li>《跑車浪漫旅 7》</li><li>《The Crew Motorfest》</li><li>《Ratchet &amp; Clank: Rift Apart》</li><li>《The First Descendant》</li><li>《The Last of Us Part II Remastered》</li><li>《FINAL FANTASY VII REBIRTH》</li><li>《地平線西域禁地》</li><li>《Marvel&#8217;s Spider-Man 2》</li></ul><p>未推出的新作方面，就有《刺客教條：暗影者》。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_55575"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6HaRMiTfvks?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>PS5 Pro Enhanced 意味着遊戲會在不同程度上有所提升，例如加入 4K 解像度材質以及 60fps 幀率，也可能加入更細緻的 8K 模式和 4K 光追模式等等，視乎開發商選擇怎樣提升遊戲。與 PS4 時代一樣，這些遊戲都會特別作出標註，而日後相信會陸續有更多遊戲加入支援 PS5 Pro Enhanced。</p><p><img decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262228" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262230" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-6-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262231" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-7-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262232" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-7-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-7.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-8-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262233" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-8-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-8.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-9-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262234" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-9-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-9.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/10/ps5-pro-announced/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">PS5 Pro 終於正式亮相　三大效能提升 + 推出日期和價格</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/10/sony-technical-presentation-sep-10/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">PlayStation 今晚 11 點有發布會　市場揣測或公佈 PS5 Pro</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/06/sony-ps-30th-seems-leak-ps5-pro/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Sony 官方隱約展示 PS5 Pro 設計　PlayStation 30 週年賀圖藏玄機</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/11/ps5-pro-enhanced/game-channel/">首批 PS5 Pro Enhanced 遊戲揭曉　完整發揮新機效能</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
